{"tid":1439893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎簽野]聯署請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織","createTime":"2019-08-10T09:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:10:24.000Z","uid":232863,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a422cfee95d7e270b9c82e4b3756a4619920110d","tid":1439893,"uid":232863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:07:50.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署請求美國國會確認香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n記得check email confirm<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KzVVQB&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=3b8efaa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KzVVQB</a><br />\nbtw希望大家平時善用不推文功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68943895_374852406434241_8186178529117863936_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_oc=AQmOzsAxL1xq5srlCuLNPbOuWeYZIxMbLn8sYR9lnNiwcAbcphvngVz8zxO-Ey4sdsw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=d0fd42b47e78c35b410c2e8c0b9329ef&amp;oe=5DD34A55\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68943895_374852406434241_8186178529117863936_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_oc%3DAQmOzsAxL1xq5srlCuLNPbOuWeYZIxMbLn8sYR9lnNiwcAbcphvngVz8zxO-Ey4sdsw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Dd0fd42b47e78c35b410c2e8c0b9329ef%26oe%3D5DD34A55&h=81e75e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">重要野,要推。永不離棄義士。核彈都唔割。保持謙虛，行動大膽\n試著說 Hit and run + Be Humble。不要說 Be water\n- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。\n------------------\n光復香港,時代革命</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ebf1fc92336dd43956266008535ac267bb2d5d10","tid":1439893,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f67fbaa7de8ae64da28f7